# how to start docker container
-> docker run [image:tag]
parameters 
    -> --name : define name for a container
    -> --rm : remove container after it has been stoped
    -> -p : this parameters will map the port of external machine to internal container ports
    -> -v : this parameters will map the volume of external machine to internal container volume
    -> -ti : run container in terminal  
    -> -d : run container in detach 

# how to stop a docker container
-> docker stop [container_name/container_id]

# how to check the running containers
-> docker ps

# how to check the all containers
-> docker ps -a

# how to start a stopped container
-> docker start [container_id/container_id]

# how to check current images in the system
-> docker images





